                    <li><p>&#9679 Code, review code, code some more</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Work with others to produce requirements and design solutions to our biggest problems</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Mentor junior engineers</p></li>
                  </ul>
                  <h5 class="text-left">Job qualifications:</h5>
                  <ul class="p" style="text-align: left;">
                    <li><p>&#9679 10+ years’ engineering experience </p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Proven history of being able to architect solutions</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Fluent in Python (for real...)</p></li>
