                    <li><p>&#9679 You’d be joining a startup. A true startup environment with all the energy and chaos that comes with it. </p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 You’d be joining the outdoor industry. We love the outdoors, outdoor gear, and getting outside.</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 We’re sort of in Denver. We’re all over the US but we’ve got a small group of us in the Denver, CO. Daily office visits aren’t mandatory but we do enjoy working together a few times a week at our rad office.</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 We’re flexible on hours, not results.    The world is becoming remote, we all have our responsibilities, and we get that. You can work the hours that make sense for you so long as you deliver at the highest level.</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 A place where your voice is valued and matters.    We’re a small, yet mighty team that works hard plays hard and moves fast. That means everyone has a seat at the table and delivers value to Out&amp;Back.</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Competitive benefits.    Health, dental and vision insurance</p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Equity: this is a senior engineering role and there will be equity provided under a typical vesting schedule in conjunction with strong performance </p></li>
                    <li><p>&#9679 Pay Range: $120,000 to $170,000 based on experience </p></li>
